text:
Yes.
I had some spare time before the lesson.

Oh, it's nothing special.
I'm aiming to be the best, after all.

But, don't overdo it.
Make sure you don't tire yourself out during the lesson.

Hehe, who do you think I am?
I know my own stamina perfectly!
Of course, I won't slack off at all during the lesson!

──Good work.
Natsuha, will you have some water?

Well then, I'll be going now.
See you later, Producer.

──Hey, Natsuha,
Are you going home dressed like that?

I'm planning to go to the gym next. Since I'll be moving
again anyway, it's more efficient to stay dressed like this, right?

...But are you okay?
You've been active all day today.

Oh, I'm fine.
Like I said earlier, I know my own stamina.
And besides, even I take breaks when needed.

Taking breaks during training is
more efficient, you know?

I see...
As long as you're resting properly...

Rest assured.
The time until I reach the gym will be a good break.

...But today,
I've decided to push my lower body to the limit.

So, I'll definitely accomplish that.
It's something I've decided for myself.

(...As expected of Natsuha...
Always aiming higher and constantly improving herself...)

(...Since I've decided to support someone like Natsuha,
I need to work hard every day so I don't get left behind...!)

Well then, see you later,
Producer.

Yeah, see you.
...Just don't push yourself too hard.

I know.
I won't do anything that would make you worry, so rest assured.

No, thank you for worrying about me.
I'm always grateful.
